# AI chat

- **Config**: provider selection and env flags — [ai-chat-config.ts](../../src/lib/ai-chat-config.ts). Preserve **gateway-first** vs OpenAI fallback behavior; do not hardcode provider choice in one place only.
- **Route**: streaming + model wiring — [route.ts](../../src/app/api/chat/route.ts).
- **Client**: streaming UI and boundaries — [chat-panel.tsx](../../src/app/(app)/chat/chat-panel.tsx) and the `(app)/chat` page. Keep heavy client logic in the panel, not in the page shell, unless the page must be client for routing reasons.
